code: public void testEquals() {     assertEquals(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread"), new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread")).     assertFalse(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread").equals(new AllPermission())).     assertFalse(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread").equals(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThreadGroup"))). }

public void testImplies() {     assertTrue(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread").implies(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread"))).     assertTrue(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThreadGroup").implies(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThreadGroup"))).     assertFalse(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread").implies(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThreadGroup"))).     assertFalse(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThreadGroup").implies(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread"))).     assertFalse(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread").implies(new AllPermission())).     assertFalse(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThreadGroup").implies(new AllPermission())).     assertTrue(new ThreadPermission("*").implies(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThread"))).     assertTrue(new ThreadPermission("*").implies(new ThreadPermission("modifyArbitraryThreadGroup"))).     assertFalse(new ThreadPermission("*").implies(new AllPermission())). }
